sbol:Collection.dcterms:title: iGEM Parts Registry
sbol:Collection.dcterms:description: The iGEM Registry is a growing collection of genetic parts that can be mixed and matched to build synthetic biology devices and systems. As part of the synthetic biology community's efforts to make biology easier to engineer, it provides a source of genetic parts to iGEM teams and academic labs.

sbol:ComponentDefinition.dcterms:title: mamE
sbol:ComponentDefinition.sbh:mutableDescription: AMB#0963; Gene function: membrane-bound serine protease required for magnetite formation; might control the localization of other magnetosome proteins
sbol:ComponentDefinition.dc:creator: Michael Brasino, Alicia Wong, Rashmi Ravichandran
sbol:ComponentDefinition.sbh:mutableProvenance: Extracted from host genome Magnetospirillum magneticum strain AMB-1

sbol:ComponentDefinition.dcterms:title: mamHI
sbol:ComponentDefinition.sbh:mutableDescription: AMB# 0961,0962; Gene function: Loss of mamI causes no membrane formation, found localization onto chains
sbol:ComponentDefinition.dc:creator: Michael Brasino, Alicia Wong, Rashmi Ravichandran
sbol:ComponentDefinition.sbh:mutableProvenance: Extracted from host genome Magnetospirillum magneticum strain AMB-1

sbol:ComponentDefinition.dcterms:title: mamJ
sbol:ComponentDefinition.sbh:mutableDescription: AMB#0964; Gene function: proper magnetosome chain organization/assembly
sbol:ComponentDefinition.dc:creator: Michael Brasino, Alicia Wong, Rashmi Ravichandran
sbol:ComponentDefinition.sbh:mutableProvenance: Extracted from host genome Magnetospirillum magneticum strain AMB-1

sbol:ComponentDefinition.dcterms:title: mamKL
sbol:ComponentDefinition.sbh:mutableDescription: AMB#0965,0966; Gene function: mamK is required for proper magnetosome chain organization; it is bacterial actin-like cytoskeleton protein required for proper alignment of the magnetosomes in a chain, shown to localize the mamI; mamL is crucial to mangneosome membrane creation, shown to be spread across the cell membrane and sometimes forms lines.
sbol:ComponentDefinition.dc:creator: Michael Brasino, Alicia Wong, Rashmi Ravichandran
sbol:ComponentDefinition.sbh:mutableProvenance: Extracted from host genome Magnetospirillum magneticum strain AMB-1
